        <hl1>Envelopes? No Problem</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>''Printing Envelopes Presents a Problem for Desktop Computers'' (Oct. 19), on the difficulty of getting Word to print envelopes, made me laugh. I recalled the recent interchange about WordPerfect vs. Word. It takes less than half as many steps to compose and print an envelope with WordPerfect, and once you've set your format it repeats faithfully each time.</p>
        <p>DAVID H. BARNHOUSE  Pittsburgh</p>
      </block>
